pageContext.claim: “They had 45,000 requests for – for 8,000 or 9,000 seats.”
pageContext.analysis: Local news reports did not report that there were 45,000 requests. The venue had room for 11,500 seats, and an estimated 2,000 people outside did not get in, the Ford Center in Evansville, Ind. said. Police estimated there were also 500 to 600 protesters.
